casebody.data:
PASSAVANT, Respondent, v. GUTLOHN et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. February 16, 1894.) Action by Herman Passavant against David Gutlohn and others.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and O’BRIEN and FOLLETT, JJ.

J. Marks, for appellants. C. Putzel, for respondent.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
